{"tid":1041380,"cid":21,"subCid":5,"title":"一人一首聽完好有感觸嘅歐美歌","createTime":"2019-02-28T19:07:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-03T14:46:47.000Z","uid":237709,"like":20,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"0caf37421efe6c991ffa5cddc16aa7806f5d13b7","tid":1041380,"uid":237709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T19:07:15.000Z","msg":"我先<br />\nPerfect Places - Lorde<br />\n<br />\n成首歌講緊一班年輕人為咗尋求美好地方<br />\n一齊party，一齊飲醉酒，一齊get high<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Let&rsquo;s kiss and then take off our clothes&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;All of the things we&rsquo;re taking &lsquo;cause we are young and we&rsquo;re ashamed&rdquo;<br />\n同人扑野、飲酒、吸毒，都係好多年輕人為咗逃離現實、尋求perfect places嘅方法。呢幾句歌詞，表面上描述班年輕人玩得有幾盡得咁盡，但係實際上講緊班年輕人因為好冇安全感，先至尋求佢哋心目中嘅perfect places。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後，Lorde用短短一句總結成首歌。<br />\n&ldquo;All the nights spent off our faces, trying to find these perfect places. Where the fuck are these perfect places anyway.&rdquo;<br />\n雖然各種逃離現實嘅方法可以令到一個人嘅情緒高漲，但係呢啲方法令到我哋變得更空虛，令我哋變得更唔完整，所以到頭來我哋又點會搵到perfect places。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然我冇party嘅習慣，但係每次聽完都好感觸，因為呢首歌正正表現出年輕人經常缺乏安全感，冇安全感先至會尋求一個perfect place。然而，一聽完最後嗰句就會覺得心up up，因為我知道呢個世界從來都唔會有perfect place。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/J0DjcsK_-HY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJ0DjcsK_-HY&d=oVHkeUedSvD9nF4ig%2BuBMITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=bca92a41\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/J0DjcsK_-HY</a>"},{"pid":"b8d34c3c0b60a366fb065175660b0a8dadbd3505","tid":1041380,"uid":237709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T19:08:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0af5479a02213205de18bf5f0487e82ad7e37d41","tid":1041380,"uid":36758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T20:02:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cmVXYOJzAJM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcmVXYOJzAJM&d=oVHkeUedSvD9nF4ig%2BuBMITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=9d6b96e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cmVXYOJzAJM</a><br />\n舊歌，成首歌就係嗰故事<br />\nSame Old Lang Syne  - Dan Fogelberg<br />\n<br />\nWe drank a toast to innocence<br />\nWe drank a toast to now<br />\nWe tried to reach beyond the emptiness<br />\nBut neither one knew how<br />\n<br />\nWe drank a toast to innocence<br />\nWe drank a toast to time<br />\nReliving, in our eloquence<br />\nAnother &quot;Auld Lang Syne&quot;<br />\n<br />\nThe beer was empty and our tongues were tired<br />\nAnd running out of things to say<br />\nShe gave a kiss to me as I got out<br />\nAnd I watched her drive away<br />\n<br />\nJust for a moment I was back at school<br />\nAnd felt that old familiar pain<br />\nAnd, as I turned to make my way back home<br />\nThe snow turned into rain"},{"pid":"d347651e9e4c113e6d4c9bbdca35c1afdb40c8db","tid":1041380,"uid":206106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T20:43:44.000Z","msg":"Skylar Grey - i will return<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nPaul walker<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過冇睇過套戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nAurora Aksnes - Through the eyes of the child<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85fadec6ccef2181975b9d2a312aae610148f30d","tid":1041380,"uid":72982,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T20:53:16.000Z","msg":"Conan Gray - Generation Why<br />\n<br />\n'Cause we are the helpless, selfish, one of a kind<br />\nMillennium kids, that all wanna die<br />\nWalking in the street with no light inside our eyes<br />\nWe are the worthless, cursed with too much time<br />\nWe get into trouble and lose our minds<br />\nSomething that I've heard a million times in my life<br />\nGeneration Why"},{"pid":"2e2e847a5677902ec7abc